{"tid":1127370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普宣布：美國退出聯合國《武器貿易條約》","createTime":"2019-04-27T05:25:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-27T05:25:34.000Z","uid":20933,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4393082e30524b7e47d0974bf56c8e6c6e2cc59a","tid":1127370,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:25:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/14e39b3f9b036d409661f8e8b03abeb26723a3e9/0_80_3120_1872/master/3120.jpg?width=1920&amp;quality=85&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=max&amp;s=f48b7b6e99cf4a36062c7bb5ce9bc7e3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.guim.co.uk%2Fimg%2Fmedia%2F14e39b3f9b036d409661f8e8b03abeb26723a3e9%2F0_80_3120_1872%2Fmaster%2F3120.jpg%3Fwidth%3D1920%26quality%3D85%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dmax%26s%3Df48b7b6e99cf4a36062c7bb5ce9bc7e3&h=14f44b36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普周五（26日）在印第安納波利斯出席「美國全國步槍協會」年會，其間宣布美國退出聯合國《武器貿易條約》（Arms Trade Treaty），稱條約侵犯美國主權，強調他不會允許外國官僚踐踏國民在憲法第二修正案中，獲確保的擁槍權。<br />\n<br />\n聯合國《武器貿易條約》於2014年12月生效，要求成員國記錄國際之間的武器轉移，禁止跨界運送可能用於侵犯人權或攻擊平民的武器，防止武器流入爆發衝突的地方。條約目前有法國、德國和英國等101個國家加入，但不包括中國和俄羅斯。<br />\n<br />\n美國前總統奧巴馬於2013年簽署，但一直未獲參議院確認。特朗普周五即場簽署文件，要求參議院終止確認《武器貿易條約》的程序。"},{"pid":"a9aa6b50d273585427252bc0ed301481e5c35bee","tid":1127370,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:25:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20190427/s00005/1556336789791/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20190427%2Fs00005%2F1556336789791%2F&d=wHiIeFeeqtLxwJ75m5qcs4PST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=d48ac1fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20190427%2Fs00005%2F1556336789791%2F&h=3670ca85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20190427/s00005/1556336789791/</a>"}]}